2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper uses machine learning techniques to solve the problem. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible sub-category as the paper proposes a deep learning approach for estimating the horizon line. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible sub-category as the paper deals with geometric constraints and contextual attributes in images. 
5. cs.RO (Robotics) is also a possible sub-category as the paper discusses the real-world applicability of the proposed method for robotics applications.
